cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE

The paper presents a denoising technique based on generative adversarial networks for improving the quality of reconstructed images for low-dose imaging conditions in synchrotron-based x-ray tomography. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). Multimedia (cs.MM) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) are also possible categories due to the use of generative adversarial networks.
